OL,3,CLack of leadership and support
OL,4,Ccriticised in review of SEND provision
OL,6,FThe Government of Jersey's provision
OL,7,Ffor children with special educational
OL,8,Fneeds and/or disabilities (SEND) lacks
OL,9,Fleadership, strategy and
OL,10,Faccountability, according to an
OL,11,Findependent report.
OL,13,FWhile there are "positive intentions
OL,14,Fand pockets of good practice", it
OL,15,Ffound that SEND services "remain
OL,16,Funderdeveloped and inconsistent", and
OL,17,Frecommendations made in a 2021 review
OL,18,F"have not yet been responded to
OL,19,Feffectively".
