OL,3,CLack of leadership and support
OL,4,Ccriticised in review of SEND provision
OL,6,FFour external experts, who have all
OL,7,Fpreviously been involved in assessing
OL,8,Fthe island's schools, conducted the
OL,9,Fsix-month review - which was
OL,10,Fcommissioned by the Government's
OL,11,FChildren, Young People, Education and
OL,12,FSkills (CYPES) department.
OL,14,FThey visited 20 schools across Jersey
OL,15,Fand surveyed hundreds of staff, pupils
OL,16,Fand parents.
OL,18,FAround two-thirds of school leaders
OL,19,Fwho responded believe SEND pupils do
OL,20,Fnot achieve as much as they should.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
