OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F385A1761074171
OL,3,CLack of leadership and support
OL,4,Ccriticised in review of SEND provision
OL,6,F"Lack of clear leadership and
OL,7,Fmanagement, coupled with changes in
OL,8,Fpriorities at the highest level, have
OL,9,Fresulted in an enduring sense of
OL,10,Fturbulence and uncertainty. This has
OL,11,Fimpeded progress.
OL,13,F"Communication is often poor. Central
OL,14,Fstaff perceive resistance to inclusion
OL,15,Ffrom some schools and schools perceive
OL,16,Fsignificant weaknesses at the centre."
OL,18,FThis can mean significant delays in
OL,19,Fidentifying the needs of individual
OL,20,Fpupils.
